AWS CloudHSM Service This is documentation for **AWS CloudHSM Classic**. For more information, see [AWS CloudHSM Classic FAQs](http://aws.amazon.com/cloudhsm/faqs-classic/), the [AWS CloudHSM Classic User Guide](https://docs.aws.amazon.com/cloudhsm/classic/userguide/), and the [AWS CloudHSM Classic API Reference](https://docs.aws.amazon.com/cloudhsm/classic/APIReference/).

**For information about the current version of AWS CloudHSM**, see [AWS CloudHSM](http://aws.amazon.com/cloudhsm/), the [AWS CloudHSM User Guide](https://docs.aws.amazon.com/cloudhsm/latest/userguide/), and the [AWS CloudHSM API Reference](https://docs.aws.amazon.com/cloudhsm/latest/APIReference/).
